    "# Credit Card Fraud Detection System\n",
    "\n",
    "## Objective\n",
    "\n",
    "The primary objective of this project is to develop a **high-performance fraud detection system** capable of identifying fraudulent transactions while minimizing disruption to legitimate users.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Problem Context\n",
    "\n",
    "Fraud detection presents several real-world challenges:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Severe class imbalance**: Fraud cases are extremely rare compared to legitimate transactions  \n",
    "- **Asymmetric costs**:\n",
    "  - False Negatives → Direct financial loss  \n",
    "  - False Positives → Customer dissatisfaction  \n",
    "- **Evolving fraud patterns**: Fraudsters continuously adapt their behavior  \n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Project Approach\n",
    "\n",
    "To address these challenges, this project focuses on:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Behavioral feature engineering\n",
    "- Comparing ensemble models (Random Forest vs XGBoost)\n",
    "- Threshold optimization for business alignment\n",
    "- Cost-sensitive evaluation\n",
    "- Model explainability using SHAP\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Key Idea\n",
    "\n",
    "> The goal is not just predictive accuracy,  \n",
    "> but building a **decision system that balances risk and customer experience**."
   ]
  },
