    "# 2. Feature Engineering\n",
    "\n",
    "## 2.1 Purpose\n",
    "\n",
    "To transform raw transaction data into features that capture **behavioral deviations**, which are key indicators of fraud.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 2.2 Feature Categories\n",
    "\n",
    "### A. Transaction Magnitude\n",
    "- `amt`, `log_amt`  \n",
    "Capture absolute and scaled transaction size\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### B. Temporal Features\n",
    "- `trans_hour`, `is_night_transaction`  \n",
    "Capture unusual transaction timing\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### C. Behavioral Aggregations\n",
    "- `customer_amt_same_day`\n",
    "- `customer_txn_same_day`\n",
    "- `prev_amt`\n",
    "\n",
    "Capture **deviation from normal behavior**\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### D. Risk Indicators\n",
    "- `category_fraud_rate`\n",
    "- `merchant_risk`\n",
    "\n",
    "Capture **historical fraud likelihood**"
